{"snp1.2:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 1.2 ","snp1.2:0.2":"Dhaniyasutta ","snp1.2:1.1":"“Pakkodano duddhakhirohamasmi, ","snp1.2:1.2":"(iti dhaniyo gopo) ","snp1.2:1.3":"Anutire mahiya samanavaso; ","snp1.2:1.4":"Channa kuti ahito gini, ","snp1.2:1.5":"Atha ce patthayasi pavassa deva”. ","snp1.2:2.1":"“Akkodhano vigatakhilohamasmi, ","snp1.2:2.2":"(iti bhagava) ","snp1.2:2.3":"Anutire mahiyekarattivaso; ","snp1.2:2.4":"Vivata kuti nibbuto gini, ","snp1.2:2.5":"Atha ce patthayasi pavassa deva”. ","snp1.2:3.1":"“Andhakamakasa na vijjare, ","snp1.2:3.2":"(iti dhaniyo gopo) ","snp1.2:3.3":"Kacche rulhatine caranti gavo; ","snp1.2:3.4":"Vutthimpi saheyyumagatam, ","snp1.2:3.5":"Atha ce patthayasi pavassa deva”. ","snp1.2:4.1":"“Baddhasi bhisi susankhata, ","snp1.2:4.2":"(iti bhagava) ","snp1.2:4.3":"Tinno paragato vineyya ogham; ","snp1.2:4.4":"Attho bhisiya na vijjati, ","snp1.2:4.5":"Atha ce patthayasi pavassa deva”. ","snp1.2:5.1":"“Gopi mama assava alola, ","snp1.2:5.2":"(iti dhaniyo gopo) ","snp1.2:5.3":"Digharattam samvasiya manapa; ","snp1.2:5.4":"Tassa na sunami kinci papam, ","snp1.2:5.5":"Atha ce patthayasi pavassa deva”. ","snp1.2:6.1":"“Cittam mama assavam vimuttam, ","snp1.2:6.2":"(iti bhagava) ","snp1.2:6.3":"Digharattam paribhavitam sudantam; ","snp1.2:6.4":"Papam pana me na vijjati, ","snp1.2:6.5":"Atha ce patthayasi pavassa deva”. ","snp1.2:7.1":"“Attavetanabhatohamasmi, ","snp1.2:7.2":"(iti dhaniyo gopo) ","snp1.2:7.3":"Putta ca me samaniya aroga; ","snp1.2:7.4":"Tesam na sunami kinci papam, ","snp1.2:7.5":"Atha ce patthayasi pavassa deva”. ","snp1.2:8.1":"“Naham bhatakosmi kassaci, ","snp1.2:8.2":"(iti bhagava) ","snp1.2:8.3":"Nibbitthena carami sabbaloke; ","snp1.2:8.4":"Attho bhatiya na vijjati, ","snp1.2:8.5":"Atha ce patthayasi pavassa deva”. ","snp1.2:9.1":"“Atthi vasa atthi dhenupa, ","snp1.2:9.2":"(iti dhaniyo gopo) ","snp1.2:9.3":"Godharaniyo paveniyopi atthi; ","snp1.2:9.4":"Usabhopi gavampatidha atthi, ","snp1.2:9.5":"Atha ce patthayasi pavassa deva”. ","snp1.2:10.1":"“Natthi vasa natthi dhenupa, ","snp1.2:10.2":"(iti bhagava) ","snp1.2:10.3":"Godharaniyo paveniyopi natthi; ","snp1.2:10.4":"Usabhopi gavampatidha natthi, ","snp1.2:10.5":"Atha ce patthayasi pavassa deva”. ","snp1.2:11.1":"“Khila nikhata asampavedhi, ","snp1.2:11.2":"(iti dhaniyo gopo) ","snp1.2:11.3":"Dama munjamaya nava susanthana; ","snp1.2:11.4":"Na hi sakkhinti dhenupapi chettum, ","snp1.2:11.5":"Atha ce patthayasi pavassa deva”. ","snp1.2:12.1":"“Usabhoriva chetva bandhanani, ","snp1.2:12.2":"(iti bhagava) ","snp1.2:12.3":"Nago putilatamva dalayitva; ","snp1.2:12.4":"Naham punupessam gabbhaseyyam, ","snp1.2:12.5":"Atha ce patthayasi pavassa deva”. ","snp1.2:13.1":"Ninnanca thalanca purayanto, ","snp1.2:13.2":"Mahamegho pavassi tavadeva; ","snp1.2:13.3":"Sutva devassa vassato, ","snp1.2:13.4":"Imamattham dhaniyo abhasatha. ","snp1.2:14.1":"“Labha vata no anappaka, ","snp1.2:14.2":"Ye mayam bhagavantam addasama; ","snp1.2:14.3":"Saranam tam upema cakkhuma, ","snp1.2:14.4":"Sattha no hohi tuvam mahamuni. ","snp1.2:15.1":"Gopi ca ahanca assava, ","snp1.2:15.2":"Brahmacariyam sugate caramase; ","snp1.2:15.3":"Jatimaranassa paragu, ","snp1.2:15.4":"Dukkhassantakara bhavamase”. ","snp1.2:16.1":"“Nandati puttehi puttima, ","snp1.2:16.2":"(iti maro papima) ","snp1.2:16.3":"Goma gohi tatheva nandati; ","snp1.2:16.4":"Upadhi hi narassa nandana, ","snp1.2:16.5":"Na hi so nandati yo nirupadhi”. ","snp1.2:17.1":"“Socati puttehi puttima, ","snp1.2:17.2":"(iti bhagava) ","snp1.2:17.3":"Goma gohi tatheva socati; ","snp1.2:17.4":"Upadhi hi narassa socana, ","snp1.2:17.5":"Na hi so socati yo nirupadhi”ti. ","snp1.2:17.6":"Dhaniyasuttam dutiyam. "}